snippet.title: EVE Gateway Official Trailer
snippet.description:
EVE Online can be difficult to get into, but in the latest update, Quadrant 3: Gateway, changes are coming. With an emphasis on both the new player experience and improvements and features for all, there has never been a better time to get into @eveonline .

Learn more at the link below:
https://www.mmorpg.com/news/eve-online-welcomes-new-players-with-big-gateway-update-epic-store-release-2000123051
